          String charsetName
          Name of the charset to use to interpret and send resources. Defaults to UTF-8

          Charset resourceCharset
          The charset to use to interpret and send resources.

        • strictMode

          boolean strictMode
          Flag to switch on the strict mode. defaults to false. In strict mode, Jawr checks that the hashcode of the bundle requested is the right one or not.

        • debugModeOn

          boolean debugModeOn
          Flag to switch on the debug mode. defaults to false.

        • debugUseRandomParam

          boolean debugUseRandomParam
          Flag to switch on the debug use random parameter. defaults to true.

        • debugOverrideKey

          String debugOverrideKey
          Key that may be passed in to override production mode

        • refreshKey

          String refreshKey
          Key that may be passed in to reload the bundles on the fly

        • gzipResourcesModeOn

          boolean gzipResourcesModeOn
          Flag to switch on the gzipped resources mode. defaults to true.

        • gzipResourcesForIESixOn

          boolean gzipResourcesForIESixOn
          Flag to switch on the gzipped resources mode for internet explorer 6. defaults to true.

        • forceCssBundleInDebugForIEOn

          boolean forceCssBundleInDebugForIEOn
          Flag to switch on css resources bundle in debug mode. defaults to false.

        • useBundleMapping

          boolean useBundleMapping
          Flag which defines if we should process the bundle at server startup. defaults to false.

        • jawrWorkingDirectory

          String jawrWorkingDirectory
          The jawr working directory path

        • servletMapping

          String servletMapping
          Servlet mapping corresponding to this config. Defaults to an empty string

        • resourceType

          String resourceType
          The type of resources handled by this config

        • allowedExtensions

          List<E> allowedExtensions
          The allowed resource extensions

        • contextPathOverride

          String contextPathOverride
          Override value to use instead of the context path of the application in generated urls. If null, contextPath is used. If blank, urls are generated to be relative.

        • contextPathSslOverride

          String contextPathSslOverride
          Override value to use instead of the context path of the application in generated urls for SSL page. If null, contextPath is used. If blank, urls are generated to be relative.

        • clientSideHandlerGeneratorClass

          String clientSideHandlerGeneratorClass
          The client side handler generator class name

        • useContextPathOverrideInDebugMode

          boolean useContextPathOverrideInDebugMode
          The flag indicating that we should use the overriden context path even in debug mode. The default value is false.

        • classpathCssHandleImage

          boolean classpathCssHandleImage
          Determines if the servlet, which provide CSS image for CSS define in the classpath should be used or not

        • imageResourcesDefinition

          String imageResourcesDefinition
          Defines the image resources definition.

        • imageHashAlgorithm

          String imageHashAlgorithm
          Defines the image hash algorithm. By default the value is CRC32. There are only 2 algorithm available CRC32 and MD5.

        • valid

          boolean valid
          Used to check if a configuration has not been outdated by a new one.

        • dwrMapping

          String dwrMapping
          Mapping path to the dwr servlet, in case it is integrated with jawr.

        • skinCookieName

          String skinCookieName
          The skin cookie name
